message: Let's be fair, Bob. I'm offering you 40% upfront.
A fair 50-50 split is better for both of us. If you reject, your next round money will be worth 10% less, while mine only 5% less. Let's be efficient and agree now.
Bob, time is money!  I'll take a smaller cut to close this deal. 55 for me, 45 for you.
